3) Program to count number of digits in given string
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
str=input('Enter string')
length=len(str)
count=0
for i in range(0,length):
    if(str[i].isdigit())==1:
        count=count+1 
print('No.of digits=',count)
------------------------------------------------
Output:
Enter string pen@100
No.of digits= 3
********************************************
